                "content": "{\"styles\": [{\"fill\": {\"alpha\": 1.0, \"content\": {\"render_type\": \"solid\", \"solid\": {\"alpha\": 1.0, \"color\": [1.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}}, \"range\": [0, 34], \"size\": 8.0, \"bold\": false, \"italic\": false, \"underline\": false, \"strokes\": [{\"content\": {\"solid\": {\"alpha\": 0.5, \"color\": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}}, \"width\": 0.004}], \"font\": {\"id\": \"7290445778273702455\", \"path\": \"C:/文轩体.ttf\"}}], \"text\": \"是不是也被这事儿给刺激到了？快去评论区投个票，看看谁的想法最吸引人！\"}",
